{"tid":1096703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌蘋果頭版無用而諗到...","createTime":"2019-04-08T01:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T03:56:22.000Z","uid":87915,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d474d72c32a3f8259731b233b792d12bb324cfcf","tid":1096703,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:35:44.000Z","msg":"話十鳩幾萬哂咗  果d 無腦言論唔屌住<br />\n但結論其實 依家香港抗爭條路 已經無乜得揀 係一個事實<br />\n<br />\n我抄人地  唔知以下無乜成本嘅方法有冇用<br />\n<br />\n前設：<br />\n1. 香港人唔鍾意付出太多<br />\n2. 香港人好懶 <br />\n3. 政府打壓港獨  集會     合法集會又要申請<br />\n<br />\n利申： 依個方法都係抄人   唔係我諗<br />\n自己係以上嘅人   自覺個方法無乜用  但已經無咩方法可以符合以上前設 又可以多人做到   <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 搵人印刷 「我要真普選 」 T Shirt  (就算唔係港獨，已經白色恐怖到有冇人敢印？） [總之港獨唔講得]<br />\n<br />\n2. 唔好以集會方式 約定某時間某區行街睇戲食飯 做私人活動   飲你嘅黑糖珍珠奶茶 <br />\n短至半個鐘都夠<br />\n<br />\n或 假期就著<br />\n<br />\n維持幾年時間<br />\n<br />\n3. 貼 「我要真普選」 喺窗口  [印象外國點埋爉燭]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似無咩用  但已經最易做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  長期好多人做就應該有noise"},{"pid":"9940fa4786e8341e4584e0e699490778e3be81a4","tid":1096703,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:17:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/08/101710_87983930b43295dd94f0788ba7af347f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F08%2F101710_87983930b43295dd94f0788ba7af347f.png&h=33fe8ab9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0d53d1631cc6612067bcc759bc3bbb545eb12cb","tid":1096703,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9940fa4786e8341e4584e0e699490778e3be81a4","tid":1096703,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:17:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/08/101710_87983930b43295dd94f0788ba7af347f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F08%2F101710_87983930b43295dd94f0788ba7af347f.png&h=33fe8ab9